{"tid":1935853,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發05:30 尚十祭壇着火！越打壓越要做，3/22 19:00尚十見","createTime":"2020-03-21T00:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T13:05:25.000Z","uid":171627,"like":87,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"eaab4800a422e824228d7725d9810db7021e4671","tid":1935853,"uid":171627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T00:34:19.000Z","msg":"突發 3/21 05:30 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尚十祭壇懷疑被縱火</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QqMcE6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQqMcE6e.jpg&h=5291a676&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7UTKwcV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7UTKwcV.jpg&h=a726f8d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CiRHhSW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCiRHhSW.jpg&h=8bc74995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nNj2hZJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnNj2hZJ.jpg&h=7ae1d497&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEGoMS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEGoMS4.jpg&h=a594816f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源: TKO公海<br />\n<br />\n尋晚先出完3月22日彥霖6個月流水式悼念會行動po<br />\n今日05:30 就着火<br />\n蠟燭仔我唔信會燒到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝救火手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽講有5，6個人行過都無反應<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">梓樂彥霖張相燒哂，磚都甩埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 嬲呀！睇完好嬲，但唔好又嬲完就算全世界3月22日同我入黎尚十悼念<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無懼白色恐怖</span></span><br />\n有巴打話「今日割五城，明日割十城」<br />\n我哋已經流水式不聚集<br />\n但最後呢？連少少空間都唔比我哋！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3月22日彥霖6個月，尚十流水式悼念行動po ！！去既同我睇哂佢，唔去都推到去既睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無諗過香港連悼念都要流水式<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1935510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1935510</a><br />\n<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"4d2ceed82fce9aeea8216cf8708026831475163b","tid":1935853,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T00:41:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c734841dca722cc7a2dfbe801f50c767576715e","tid":1935853,"uid":52705,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T00:43:40.000Z","msg":"仲要呢幾日咁撚潮濕有咩可能自己燒到咁，一定有外來因素"},{"pid":"0d787f603f866976e512749c7badac4e427c7ca8","tid":1935853,"uid":176027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T00:44:34.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhhh"},{"pid":"d3f17b9af0f71baa8eba7814d537b07325d66755","tid":1935853,"uid":171107,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T00:46:16.000Z","msg":"死人都唔放過"},{"pid":"91d33be41b0a0b50671c6a147ec085af4a7c4b8f","tid":1935853,"uid":171627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c734841dca722cc7a2dfbe801f50c767576715e","tid":1935853,"uid":52705,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T00:43:40.000Z","msg":"仲要呢幾日咁撚潮濕有咩可能自己燒到咁，一定有外來因素"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T00:47:16.000Z","msg":"一定！<br />\n無可能蠟燭仔燒到咁高！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全世界3月22尚十見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br